<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>解答；解决方法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Here is the <strong>perfect solution to</strong> all your problems.
这是解决你所有问题的最佳方法。</p><footer>北师大④ – 10</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The school advisors help you talk through your problems but they don’t give you any direct <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (solve).  （2010 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. solution  </p></div>